Diane Duane's book (while not considered completely canon material by Paramount) is the default &quot;bible&quot; of Romulan fandom. <br>
<br>
Very few people realize this, but.... LOTS of the words she invented in THAT book was eventually adopted into the Star Trek films and episodes.  The book was published way back in 1987, where she invented the Rommie greeting &quot;Jolan Tru&quot; <br>
